steps:
To find two integers \( x \) between 1 and 100 that satisfy the given conditions, we need to solve the following system of congruences:
\[ \begin{cases} 
x \equiv 3 \pmod{4} \\ 
x \equiv 1 \pmod{3} \\ 
x \equiv 1 \pmod{5} 
